data.description: Seller has an unconditional assumable loan at a rate of 3.125 …***When using approved lender buyer may receive 1% lower than market interest rate utilizing our lender paid temporary buy down.  Welcome Home! This is an extraordinary opportunity. Cape Cod nestled on 6 acres with approx. 3128 sq ft. main level living. Kitchen is open concept to the living room with a breakfast nook making this a spectacular entertaining space. Unwind and relax on the covered front porch, Upstairs can also be a master suite.  The current homeowners have their business equipment on the right side of their property, and they also have the back portion of the yard fenced for the goats, horses welcome. move in ready country living at its best.  This house is family sub-dividable, close to Lake Anna and located about 20 minutes from Route 95, Route 29, Route 1, Route 3. Artesian Well   Sellers are Motivated!  Sellers are MOTIVATED!!
